{"tid":273633,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實酒精令毒撚更傷心 洗撚你講","createTime":"2017-06-06T17:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T18:03:59.000Z","uid":58344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70fbd4e0ffcec52d9ee6123e4affb20a0ececadd","tid":273633,"uid":58344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:07:33.000Z","msg":"又係我呢條煩撚廢撚開post了<br />\n我幾年拒絕左幾個女仔 已經真心毒了<br />\nEx打擊太大  雙面人扮堅強真係好幸苦<br />\n<br />\n我已經試過扮冇野搵話題揾ex了 但佢根本唔在乎<br />\n我用盡所有方法了 引起唔到佢注意<br />\n佢已經係外國差不多一年半了<br />\n我都無停滯不前 工作學業都再向上游麻醉自己 <br />\n以為可以分散自己 但人生已經唔知為咩咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想屌我就屌我啦 我今晩已經哭了 幾年未試過了<br />\n勿相認 原諒我已經醉 <br />\n<br />\n我偏想到偏頭痛 蠢不蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3881266f827c32d181b9056f55b9bc46ce52b206","tid":273633,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:16:23.000Z","msg":"趁以家清下bucket list放鬆下個人 清下清下連唔開心都清埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋世界上咁多女 為左一條女 值得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過銀行都多錢啦 d錢都唔會係你架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581a755c670933e821d1b56334a95afd8563a60a","tid":273633,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:25:25.000Z","msg":"有ex仲話自己係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb12205e4a51808f0d1c1b3cf50a0548bd259421","tid":273633,"uid":58344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:39:30.000Z","msg":"我都已經唔知自己人生為咩<br />\n我都知唔值 但自己不停係咁 <br />\n以前唔係 唔代表宜家唔係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以為清醒好痛苦 原來酒精之後仲痛苦<br />\n你的金剛圈　最好箍得更緊<br />\n令我的下世　記得有過今生"},{"pid":"b84f2d544ee03f6cf79a188b65a2918f3d21cfe4","tid":273633,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"盡情飲啦<br />\n我一星期都飲幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41a35e8dc994cd722c1b7b3338184741ff1ed04","tid":273633,"uid":58344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:44:09.000Z","msg":"今晚喝多了<br />\n不知道為什麼哭出來了 男人老狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3f5f5e885fcd2c9029f2c299f0525a332d1c1b","tid":273633,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:48:13.000Z","msg":"連續飲左兩星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02686b158bdd566e645188bbe6febe333f06dc53","tid":273633,"uid":58344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:03:59.000Z","msg":"三界唯心 萬法唯識<br />\n我以為了解當中道理 <br />\n今日已經破介 再自我麻醉"}]}